elements combined unexpectedly last Friday at the Rainbow Family
Gathering in Arizona, when the Rainbows' unarmed peacekeepers
captured a suspect wanted in a brutal Florida murder case. By
HANNAH MILLER. Story will move in the ``A'' setion. &QL; 
