<DATE_TIME> 1998-07-09 13:23 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7280 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-WHITE-COLUMN-BOS &LR;      07-09 0631
