<HEADLINE>
ART THAT STANDS ON ITS OWN 2 WHEELS 
</HEADLINE>
  (DUPLICATION WARNING: Also filed in `a' and `f' category.) 
(mk) 
 By JIM McCRAW   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   NEW YORK _ While the art community may look upon ``The Art of
