   WENATCHEE-LEGAL (Undated) It's a powerful team.They're national
experts in police misconduct, mental health abuse, civil rights and
DNA evidence. They've fought and won some of the hottest legal
battles in the state. They've gotten convictions overturned for
scores wrongly convicted of murder, rape and other major crimes.
Now they're teaming up with law students and professors to try to
get new trials for 15 men and women convicted of child sex crimes
in Wenatchee.
</P>
<P>
   By Andrew Schneider. (story will move in the ``a'' category)
</P>
