Griffey Jr. because he says Griffey backed out of a deal to open a
chain of restaurants. The civil suit was filed in September. The
Griffey family attorney will present arguments to dismiss the case
July 24 in King County Superior Court in Seattle.
</P>
<P>
   By Angelo Bruscas and Ronald Tillery. (story will move in the
``s'' category)
</P>
<P>
   BBA-COLUMN-VECSEY (Seattle) From the Mariners-Angels game.
