</P>
<P>
   TOBACCO-TALKS (Undated) _ Three weeks of secret negotiations
between the states attorneys general and the tobacco companies have
broken down. By Barry Meier. (Scheduled to move by 9 p.m. ET in
``a'' news file.)
</P>
<P>
   WORLD-COURT-U.S. (Rome) _ In its most detailed presentation to
date, the United States set out new conditions Thursday for taking
part in an international criminal court that would sharply limit
the tribunal's scope and authority. By Alessandra Stanley.
</P>
<P>
   NY-MISSING MILLIONAIRE (New York) _ Developments on the story of
a missing wealthy widow. (Scheduled to move by 9 p.m. ET in ``a''
news file.)
</P>
