<P>
   IRS-OVERHAUL (Washington) _ The Senate overwhelmingly approves a
compromise plan designed to make sweeping changes at the Internal
Revenue Service. The Senate voted 96-2 to adopt an IRS
restructuring plan that lawmakers hope will provide taxpayers with
greater protections while reining in potential abuses. By DAVID
IVANOVICH.
</P>
