the criticism from fans and media, mediated the internal squabbling
among his talented but ego-driven superstars, and guided his team
to the lip of its fifth World Cup championship. Yet Zagallo still
hears little but second-guessing from Brazil's ardent fans. By JOHN
P. LOPEZ.
</P>
<P>
